## Notes
- digest differs between runtimes (bash uses Python sha256 on raw string; pwsh
  uses .NET SHA256 on the same string — cross-platform line-ending differences
  produce different hashes). Determinism is per-runtime, which is what matters:
  each verdict JSON will carry the digest from whichever tool produced the bundle.
- PP-007 (SDD_SUDO path) uses SDD_SUDO_SKIP_SIG=1 test scaffolding; full HMAC
  verification is implemented but requires a key to be present.
